as per your request.

33
00:02:00,190 --> 00:02:02,410
Why did you buy so many things?

34
00:02:03,151 --> 00:02:05,389
Mr. Xiao said your body
has been weak lately.

35
00:02:05,390 --> 00:02:08,331
He instructed me
to buy these tonics for you.

36
00:02:08,431 --> 00:02:09,851
Thank you, Uncle Xiang.

37
00:02:13,711 --> 00:02:15,870
Do you think I have a large appetite?

38
00:02:15,871 --> 00:02:18,210
