preparations for the game too.

55
00:03:06,510 --> 00:03:07,949
Besides the rules that were mentioned,

56
00:03:07,950 --> 00:03:10,349
I also came up with
a special rule for you.

57
00:03:10,350 --> 00:03:12,430
I'll kiss you whenever you mention

58
00:03:12,431 --> 00:03:13,891
the game project.

59
00:03:14,871 --> 00:03:16,810
Will you mention it again?

60
00:03:22,670 --> 00:03:24,210
That's more like it.

61
00:03:25,031 --> 00:03:27,270
I plan to cook for you.

62
00:03:27,271 --> 00:03:29,691
I'll make you
some snow pear and white fungus soup.

63
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:32,370
